embeds.title: Open a Ticket
embeds.description:
**When opening a ticket**, please immediately send the topic of your ticket, as well as any related usernames, User IDs, and proof.

# Ticket Guidelines
When creating a ticket, please follow these guidelines to ensure your issue or request is handled as swiftly as possible. Failing to comply may result in your **ticket being closed**, a **moderation action being taken against you**, or you being **blacklisted from our ticketing system**.

## Stay Respectful
We understand that series of events leading up to you opening a ticket may be frustrating, but our staff are here to help. Do not insult our staff, and try to comply as much as possible.
